---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us - AIPlatformDataSecurity">
  <div class="hero">
    <h1>About AIPlatformDataSecurity</h1>
    <p class="hero-subtitle">Empowering IT Security Professionals Since 2019</p>
  </div>

  <section class="content">
    <div class="mission-section">
      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        To create a global community of IT security professionals who are committed to continuous learning, constructive criticism, and professional growth. We believe that honest feedback and rigorous learning standards are essential for developing world-class security expertise.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="vision-section">
      <h2>Our Vision</h2>
      <p>
        To become the premier platform for IT security professionals who want to challenge themselves, learn from peers worldwide, and develop the thick skin necessary to thrive in the demanding field of cybersecurity.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="values-section">
      <h2>Our Values</h2>
      <div class="values-grid">
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>üéØ Accountability</h3>
          <p>We hold each other accountable to high learning standards and professional excellence.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>üí™ Resilience</h3>
          <p>We believe in building mental toughness through constructive criticism and honest feedback.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>üåç Global Perspective</h3>
          <p>Our diverse, worldwide community brings different perspectives and experiences to security challenges.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>üìö Continuous Learning</h3>
          <p>We embrace the mindset that learning never stops in the rapidly evolving field of cybersecurity.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>ü§ù Mutual Support</h3>
          <p>Despite our direct approach, we support each other's growth and celebrate collective achievements.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>üòÑ Balanced Approach</h3>
          <p>We balance serious learning with humor and fun, creating an engaging community environment.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="history-section">
      <h2>Our History</h2>
      <div class="timeline">
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-year">2019</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>The Beginning</h3>
            <p>AIPlatformDataSecurity was founded as a WhatsApp group for IT professionals seeking serious, no-nonsense learning opportunities in cybersecurity.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-year">2020</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>Global Expansion</h3>
            <p>The group expanded internationally, attracting members from different continents and diverse technical backgrounds.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-year">2021</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>Structured Learning</h3>
            <p>Introduced formal learning schedules and accountability measures to ensure consistent professional development.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-year">2022</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>Community Growth</h3>
            <p>Reached significant milestones in member engagement and successful career transitions within the community.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-year">2023</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>Digital Presence</h3>
            <p>Launched YouTube channel and expanded online presence to reach more security professionals.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-year">2024</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>Official Website</h3>
            <p>Launched our official website to better serve our community and provide resources for members.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="leadership-section">
      <h2>Leadership</h2>
      <div class="leader-card">
        <h3>Joe M - "JoeVirus"</h3>
        <p class="leader-title">Founder & Community Moderator</p>
        <p>
          Joe M is the founder and driving force behind AIPlatformDataSecurity. Known for his direct communication style and unwavering commitment to excellence, Joe has created a unique learning environment that has helped hundreds of IT professionals advance their careers. His philosophy of "You are as good as your last movie. Keep your brags fresh" has become a cornerstone of the community culture.
        </p>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/joem75/" target="_blank" class="linkedin-link">
          Connect with Joe on LinkedIn
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: var(--gradient-secondary);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    animation: slideInDown 0.8s ease-out;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(240, 147, 251, 0.3);
  }

  @keyframes slideInDown {
    from {
      transform: translateY(-50px);
      opacity: 0;
    }
    to {
      transform: translateY(0);
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .mission-section,
  .vision-section,
  .values-section,
  .history-section,
  .leadership-section {
    background-color: var(--card-bg);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }

  .mission-section h2,
  .vision-section h2,
  .values-section h2,
  .history-section h2,
  .leadership-section h2 {
    color: var(--accent-color);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.75rem;
  }

  .values-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .value-card {
    background-color: var(--bg-color);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out;
    animation-fill-mode: both;
  }

  .value-card:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
  .value-card:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
  .value-card:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
  .value-card:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.4s; }
  .value-card:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
  .value-card:nth-child(6) { animation-delay: 0.6s; }

  .value-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px) scale(1.03);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 35px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
    border-color: var(--tertiary-accent);
  }

  @keyframes fadeInUp {
    from {
      transform: translateY(30px);
      opacity: 0;
    }
    to {
      transform: translateY(0);
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }

  .value-card h3 {
    background: var(--gradient-success);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .value-card p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .timeline {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .timeline-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
    animation: slideInRight 0.8s ease-out;
    animation-fill-mode: both;
  }

  .timeline-item:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
  .timeline-item:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
  .timeline-item:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
  .timeline-item:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.4s; }
  .timeline-item:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
  .timeline-item:nth-child(6) { animation-delay: 0.6s; }

  @keyframes slideInRight {
    from {
      transform: translateX(50px);
      opacity: 0;
    }
    to {
      transform: translateX(0);
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }

  .timeline-year {
    background: var(--gradient-tertiary);
    color: white;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    min-width: 80px;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(79, 172, 254, 0.4);
  }

  .timeline-content {
    flex: 1;
    background-color: var(--bg-color);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .timeline-content:hover {
    transform: translateX(10px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(156, 136, 255, 0.3);
    border-color: var(--purple-accent);
  }

  .timeline-content h3 {
    color: var(--accent-color);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .timeline-content p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .leader-card {
    background-color: var(--bg-color);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .leader-card h3 {
    color: var(--accent-color);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .leader-title {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .linkedin-link {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--gradient-success);
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(67, 233, 123, 0.4);
  }

  .linkedin-link:hover {
    background: var(--gradient-tertiary);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(56, 249, 215, 0.6);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .values-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .timeline-item {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .timeline-year {
      align-self: flex-start;
    }
  }
</style>